<paragraph blockId="39.[151,1436,1367,1752]" pageId="39" pageNumber="40">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,317,1655,1680]" pageId="39" pageNumber="40">Remarks:</emphasis>
This species was first recorded as 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Fabricius" baseAuthorityYear="1781" box="[724,876,1655,1680]" class="Insecta" family="Crabronidae" genus="Stizus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="39" pageNumber="40" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="tridens">
<emphasis box="[724,876,1655,1680]" italics="true" pageId="39" pageNumber="40">Stizus tridens</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by 
<bibRefCitation author="Morice" box="[924,1092,1655,1680]" pageId="39" pageNumber="40" refString="Morice, F. (1921) Annotated lists of Aculeate Hymenoptera (except Heterogyna) and Chrysids recently collected in Mesopotamia and North-West Persia. The Journal of the Bombay Natural History Society, 27, 816 - 828." type="journal article" year="1921">Morice (1921)</bibRefCitation>
. Two subspecies, 
<taxonomicName authority="Radoszkowski, 1887" authorityName="Radoszkowski" authorityYear="1887" class="Insecta" family="Crabronidae" genus="Bembecinus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="39" pageNumber="40" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="tridens" subSpecies="cyanescens">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="39" pageNumber="40">Bembecinus tridens cyanescens</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Radoszkowski" box="[389,632,1692,1717]" pageId="39" pageNumber="40" refString="Radoszkowski, O. (1887) Faune hymenopterologique transcaspienne (Suite). Horae societatis Entomologicae Rossicae, 21, 88 - 101." type="journal article" year="1887">Radoszkowski, 1887</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
(de 
<bibRefCitation author="Beaumont" box="[702,891,1692,1716]" pageId="39" pageNumber="40" refString="De Beaumont, J. (1970) Sphecidae de l'Iran (Hym.) (Resultats de voyages entomologiques deWilli Richter, Stuttgart, en Iran, en 1954 et 1956). Stuttgarter Beitrage zur Naturkunde aus dem Staatlichen Museum fur Naturkunde in Stuttgart, 220, 1 - 18." type="journal article" year="1970">Beaumont 1970</bibRefCitation>
) and 
<taxonomicName authority="tridens" authorityName="Gussakovskii" authorityYear="1935" box="[974,1295,1692,1717]" class="Insecta" family="Crabronidae" genus="Bembicinus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="39" pageNumber="40" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="tridens" subSpecies="tridens">
